{"tid":493532,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一套好耐之前睇過既西片，唔知名，搵左好多年","createTime":"2017-12-08T15:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T03:43:14.000Z","uid":114693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5663f7512e9ef745d86010acd5a9810ac1c81575","tid":493532,"uid":114693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"個故仔係話一班玩開既細路入面有個新加入既肥仔，但唔受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n有一次，佢地去樹林玩，因為個肥仔有相機，就叫埋佢去。之後上左隻細船仔，但個肥仔失平衡跌左落水，佢地無人救佢掛住笑，跟住佢真係浸死左。<br />\n<br />\n班人因為太驚比人發現，夾手夾腳埋左佢條屍，應承唔向人透露。返去之後，個肥仔唔見左，屋企人去報警，就查佢地，逐個逐個審，就開始驚有人爆大獲。好似最後有人太驚，爆左岀黎。<br />\n<br />\n淨係記得呢啲，當時仲係200X年無意中係now睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想搵返 唔知點解搵唔到有一種傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a123da328d0bd3f731af1ba4d9f73ae7f8830c1","tid":493532,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"「name of film forest wood camera chubby boy drowned bury children」<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 咗陣搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n或者樓主自己嘗試一下再修飾一下啲英文字詞，我都係根據你嘅中文關鍵字搵"},{"pid":"7b5accdd07c77d312a987b7ab7ba55c084657851","tid":493532,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6951e105c1678c912ca08df39d93d99e6c032eee","tid":493532,"uid":114693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"我一直向now個方面搵，原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}